hat will attract traffic to your site.\n\nDon''t hide the fact that you earn money on purchases made using your affiliate link. Many of your visitors will be pros that recognize undisclosed affiliate links, and they will spread the word if you are not honest. You''ll get more business from customers and affiliates by being honest and credible.\n\nYou should not be looking to steal customers from others, but instead present your own business as the best option to fulfill any potential customer''s needs. Applying the advice contained in this article will allow you to succeed in your affiliate marketing endeavors.', 'Want To Learn More About Affiliate Marketing?  Read This!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision', '', '', '2012-01-14 13:36:32', '2012-01-14 13:36:32', '', 20, 'http://yourwebsitedomain.com/20-revision/22/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(23, 1, '2012-01-14 13:38:58', '2012-01-14 13:38:58', '<a href="http://yourwebsitedomain.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/affiliate-marketing1.jpg"><img src="http://yourwebsitedomain.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/affiliate-marketing1.jpg" alt="" title="affiliate-marketing1" width="400" height="300" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-24" /></a>You need to study affiliate marketing and gain skills in it, in order to profit from it. Learning as much as you can will maximize the profits you make from affiliate marketing. By reading this article, you will have everything you need for a good start.\r\n\r\nWatch out for vendors who will attempt to scam you by convincing you to apply their tracking system to your site. Avoid any trouble by using a respected, professional tracking system.\r\n\r\nYou need to find out exactly how all orders are tracked before signing with any marketing programs. If the company doesn''t track your sales well, you may lose out on commission.\r\n\r\nGain the trust of your readers. If your readers begin to like you, they will try to support you through your affiliate marketing attempts.\r\n\r\nMany affiliate marketing strategies, highly effective ones, rely on building backlinks to your site. You must not employ backlinks that dump visitors onto a page they were not expecting, though. If links to your site are referencing Kindles, yet the link refers to an iPod page, your customers become dissatisfied. This type of strategy may seem smart, but it will backfire, as customers may view you as dishonest.\r\n\r\nJust because you are making money as an affiliate marketer, don''t get complacent about why you have achieved. Striving for new and improved things never hurts. Keep finding new income sources and ways to improve your current ones. Consider adding a new affiliate program to the mix or try creating YouTube videos to pull in new customers. Always keep striving for success.\r\n\r\nIn order to make good business decisions, you need up-to-the-minute sales analysis. Real time statistics allow you to keep track of how much traffic you have had to your site. You can compare this number with the number of people who made purchases.\r\n\r\nMake sure that the affiliate company you are considering offers commissions for all the kinds of sales that they offer. How will orders placed over the telephone, by post, or by fax be tracked? Be certain you are receiving the funds that you are owed.\r\n\r\nPictures of the product as well as reviews from product owners is helpful to prospective customers. If you can provide more information to potential customers, they will feel more comfortable about a purchasing decision. They may even refer other customers to your business.\r\n\r\nIf you take the time to plan your next move and keep these tips in mind, you are going to see the positive outcome that you were hoping for when you decided to get involved. So make a action plan - including these tips - and get to work!', 'Are You Thinking About Affiliate Marketing?  Try These Great Ideas!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'are-you-thinking-about-affiliate-marketing-try-these-great-ideas', '', '', '2012-01-14 13:38:58', '2012-01-14 13:38:58', '', 0, 'http://yourwebsitedomain.com/?p=23', 0, 'post', '', 0),
