(25, 1, '2012-01-14 13:37:59', '2012-01-14 13:37:59', '', 'Are You Thinking About Affiliate Marketing?  Try These Great Ideas!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision', '', '', '2012-01-14 13:37:59', '2012-01-14 13:37:59', '', 23, 'http://yourwebsitedomain.com/23-revision/25/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(26, 1, '2012-01-15 13:39:04', '2012-01-15 13:39:04', '<a href="http://yourwebsitedomain.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/affiliate-marketing2.jpg"><img src="http://yourwebsitedomain.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/affiliate-marketing2.jpg" alt="" title="affiliate-marketing2" width="452" height="265" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-27" /></a>Affiliate marketing is a great way to make money online. People doing business online have been using it to earn profits for years. With so much history and ongoing development, it is easy to find a great deal of useful information about affiliate marketing. Whether you are just starting out, or are experienced in affiliate marketing, these tips will be useful to you.\r\n\r\nChoose a niche product or industry to increase your affiliate marketing profits. You can immediately see profits through specialty niches as opposed to main stream products that may take longer to see profits.\r\n\r\nMake sure your affiliates match the type of person who visits your site. Make sure that the advertising on your site matches what your site is selling. Keep in mind that your site visitors are there for a specific purpose. Make the most out of that, and post advertisements that can fill their needs.\r\n\r\nDisclose the fact that you profit from readers clicking on affiliate links. Your readers know an affiliate link when they see it and trying to hide the fact will just make them not trust you. Through this act of integrity your business is surely to grow.\r\n\r\nMarketing the web''s most in demand products may not be the best for you as an affiliate. Don''t confuse quality with popularity. Choosing very popular products means you will be in fierce competition with other affiliates. A profit may not occur in this instance.\r\n\r\nInstead of trying to offer visitors something they''ve never seen before, stick with what has already been proven as a good seller. A lot of webmasters avoid the most popular affiliate marketing products, thinking that the competition will be too tough to deal with. However, if the niche is extremely popular it might be easier to make sales and be more profitable than a niche that isn''t popular. Additionally, the more popular the product is, the more buyers that are going to be available wanting to buy it. Despite have to deal with competitors, it is still possible to make good sales in this situation. All you need to do to grab and hold their attention, is to find something that sets you above the rest of the crowd.\r\n\r\nAffiliate marketing offers plenty of money-making opportunities. It is just like any other marketing venture in the sense that research, education, and knowledge are the keys to developing a proficient grasp of the inner workings of the business and maximizing your profit potential.', 'Make The Most Of Your Affiliate Marketing: Suggestions And Tips', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'make-the-most-of-your-affiliate-marketing-suggestions-and-tips', '', '', '2012-01-14 13:40:28', '2012-01-14 13:40:28', '', 0, 'http://yourwebsitedomain.com/?p=26', 0, 'post', '', 0),
