(29, 1, '2012-01-14 14:40:39', '2012-01-14 14:40:39', '<a href="http://yourwebsitedomain.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/affiliate-marketing3.jpg"><img src="http://yourwebsitedomain.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/affiliate-marketing3.jpg" alt="" title="affiliate-marketing3" width="400" height="300" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-30" /></a>Affiliate market programs may appear difficult to set up, but it may not be as confusing as it first appears. Web referral tech has made great leaps in effectiveness and can bring ease and savings to your program. Use the informative tips found in the article below to guide you in the needed steps to get started in affiliate marketing.\r\n\r\nWhen you are considering an affiliate program, make sure you understand how they pay their commissions. Sometimes there are special rules or exceptions you need to know about. Ensure that the tracking system is capable of handling all types of orders, including Internet, telephone, mail and fax. Do not work with a company that does not have the ability to track all of your work. This could result in you not being paid fairly for the work you have done!\r\n\r\nFor those who have ad banners, try posing an interesting question that would only be answered if a visitor goes to your site. That banner with a question will tempt a lot of viewers into clicking. Give discounts to whichever site visitors get the question correct.\r\n\r\nWhen picking an affiliate company, choose one with many options for payment as this allows you to get your money quickly. You will find companies paying by PayPal or AlertPay, as well as companies that only mail checks at specific thresholds in earnings.\r\n\r\nOnly get profitable affiliates. Keep an eye on your affiliates to make sure that they are performing well. If you remove the affiliates who are performing badly, you can focus on affiliates that are making you money.\r\n\r\nPublish hand written advertisements on your website. Handwritten content adds a touch of something that people feel is more personal. Buyers love seeing that there really is a living human behind the page somewhere. Does your handwriting look like a scribble? Find someone whose writing is clear.\r\n\r\n100 percent commission programs are not always a scam as you might assume. Do some research and read all the fine print before dismissing the program. A 100 percent commission is generally offered because they keep the subscription costs while you pay upfront sales costs. You can still make money from these programs, so examine all of the details before writing them off.\r\n\r\nAs you may now understand, engaging in an affiliate marketing program does not need to be as complex or expensive as it once was. Applying the tips from this article before creating your affiliate marketing program can really help you to be successful.', 'Looking For Effective Affiliate Marketing Strategies? Here''s Some Advice!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'looking-for-effective-affiliate-marketing-strategies-heres-some-advice', '', '', '2012-01-14 13:41:51', '2012-01-14 13:41:51', '', 0, 'http://yourwebsitedomain.com/?p=29', 0, 'post', '', 0),
