(33, 1, '2012-01-14 13:43:24', '2012-01-14 13:43:24', '<a href="http://yourwebsitedomain.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Affiliate-Marketing4.jpg"><img src="http://yourwebsitedomain.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Affiliate-Marketing4.jpg" alt="" title="Affiliate-Marketing4" width="400" height="300" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-34" /></a>Affiliate marketing may seem tedious and complex, but if you are smart about it, you can make serious money. However, do not worry. The following tips will help you avoid some of the common pitfalls.\r\n\r\nGive careful consideration before linking to products on your site. Arranging the affiliate links you have on your site may take some time, but presentation is an important factor in increasing your profits.\r\n\r\nToo many banners make a site appear confusing so try to avoid overusing them. If your site looks to pushy and unprofessional, then people will not want to visit your site. Don''t let the banners on your site contain all the information, your content should be the most informative part.\r\n\r\nTo get ahead of your competitors, get a good number of Google Plus fans following you. Integrate Google Plus into your site and into your other social networking circles. Make sure your content provides customers an incentive to follow your site.\r\n\r\nYou can tell customers on your site that they can become an affiliate as well. When they purchase your product, ask them if they would like to earn some money by selling it for you. If your customer chooses be your affiliate, that one sale can lead to thousands of sales. This can help you get a big increase in profits and you will have better affiliate marketing as well.\r\n\r\nBecause Google and other companies put special focus on social media websites, it is imperative that you do the same. The search engines use the links on social media websites to help determine search rankings. Linking to sites like Twitter and Facebook along with a comment section and tweets will help your site get recognized.\r\n\r\nAlways consider your target customers when choosing items for affiliate marketing techniques. You can sell cheap products in large volumes by offering low-click-through options. More expensive products call for more intense, focused selling, to raise the ratio of customers versus visitors.\r\n\r\nYou should always be honest when participating in affiliate marketing, and you will find that the people who visit your site will be affected in a positive way. When you are doing affiliate marketing, remember that honesty is important. If your readers see that you are marketing your products in good faith, they are far more likely to respond positively and buy your products.\r\n\r\nAs you are now aware, affiliate marketing is simpler than it first appears. Though it requires study and hard work, plus reaching out to a network, the benefits to your business will make it worthwhile. Keep these ideas in mind in order to have more affiliate marketing success.', 'Try These Tips If You Want To Succeed In Affiliate Marketing', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'try-these-tips-if-you-want-to-succeed-in-affiliate-marketing', '', '', '2012-01-14 13:43:24', '2012-01-14 13:43:24', '', 0, 'http://yourwebsitedomain.com/?p=33', 0, 'post', '', 0),
